            "circlet_of_logos": {
              "desc": "<p>草木的主神赠送的冠冕，曾在迷宫的王之间代代相传，最终由王的侍者继承。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/24/36540823/11abc6739dff1cf50b95b394a3462162_4827972428504820888.png",
